# GENERAL INFORMATION\
\
*Title of dataset: \cf2 \expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
China's Global Environmental Leadership (CGEL) Database (Version 1.0)\
\
*Dataset description: The CGEL database systematically documents cross-border environmental governance initiatives led by Chinese state and non-state actors from 2000 to 2024. It is, to the authors' knowledge, the first database of its kind to collect granular, initiative-level data on China's environmental leadership activities in international arenas. The database contains 291 initiatives and 29 variables per initiative, covering initiative characteristics, target environmental problems, governance functions, and the Chinese and international actors involved.\
\cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \
*Unit of analysis: \cf2 \expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
A governance initiative \'97 a cross-border, China-led initiative that meets the inclusion criteria below.\
\
