\cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 # DATA COLLECTION, VALIDATION, AND CODING\
\
*Data collection: \cf2 \expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Cases were identified through three complementary methods: (1) systematic searches across six existing databases on global environmental governance; (2) a scoping review of academic and grey literature on China in global environmental governance; and (3) expert consultation. All candidate cases were screened by at least two researchers to confirm eligibility and remove duplicates.\
\cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \
*Quality: \cf2 \expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Each initiative was independently coded by at least two coders. Disagreements were resolved through structured deliberation, with reference to original sources. Unresolved cases were escalated to a full-team review. All coding decisions are archived.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 Although the authors cannot claim the 291 initiatives are exhaustive, this is to their knowledge the most comprehensive database tracking China's leadership activities in global environmental governance.\
\pard\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \
*Key coding convention:\
